      "Provide specific file paths and repository names in your answer.",
      "Write your findings to /workspace/answer.json."
    ],
    "success_definition": "Agent successfully identifies relevant files and symbols across all repos in the hashicorp-vault fixture.",
    "seed_prompt": "Audit Vault secret-engine access control. Find the Go source files in hashicorp/vault that (1) register or dispatch secret-engine backends, (2) gate secret-engine operations on capabilities or path policy checks, and (3) emit the deny path when a caller crosses an auth boundary."
